{"tid":1204280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人可以為香港做啲咩？","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:23:29.000Z","uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b33a478a6bd2e568e1266b32dd0cec0ff405c1f","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"香港人可以為香港做啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，<br />\n如果你真係叫自己香港人 ，<br />\n唔好再比藉口自己 ，<br />\n你一定有意務為香港出一分力，即使係再少再薄弱嘅力量，我地積少成多。<br />\n明白每個人都有所顧慮，<br />\n但一定好過你坐係屋企就咁講句加油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前線: <br />\n1. 抗爭:<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦，做得嘅相信已經出左去，多謝你地每一位為香港衝鋒陷陣。<br />\n<br />\n2. 通訊:<br />\n絕對需要有人係中間幫手傳遞訊息，連接前排抗爭同後排補給人士。<br />\n<br />\n3. 急救:<br />\n如果你有醫學背景，有讀過急救課程，希望你可以提供你嘅腦袋。<br />\n<br />\n4. 補給(裝備+物資): <br />\n加入任何一個小組去幫手，人手永遠唔會嫌多。唔上場做後援嘅亦可以提供捐贈物品。即使身處海外嘅香港人都無藉口，捐款。<br />\n- <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197358</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後援<br />\n如果你有其他顧慮或問題而上唔到場，我相信你一定仲有其他野可以為香港做。<br />\n<br />\n1. 文宣:<br />\n整合第一資訊，分享內容。<br />\n<br />\n2. 戰術:<br />\n集思廣益，如果再有事件發生影響前線運作，我地可以點做？ (例如無理搜身事件，點樣避過搜查提供物資去前線)<br />\n<br />\n3. 罷工、罷市、罷課<br />\n<br />\n4. 海外人士<br />\n分享分享同分享，令全世界人士關注呢件事。<br />\n- Telegram group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/By4bJhMzpyWuzEGroG3awQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBy4bJhMzpyWuzEGroG3awQ&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=71a3dd8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/By4bJhMzpyWuzEGroG3awQ</a><br />\n- 外語資訊post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202892</a>"},{"pid":"46aeca301687a7d1c37dbd28ce23962d3aeb8d71","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"被無理搜身要注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203590</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"100b8a61fffc09f764315691b0ed29082a7b468b","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9c46f40c138e9f1b1103c035eafd62b1990f70d","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f41cfc14ecf76c575d9d86dd878f36f829d2351e","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"552e22d5979f25a0163f26d55e8ec31498944b2d","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"應付地鐵站無理搜身<br />\n<br />\n1. 上前一大班人主動被佢搜<br />\n<br />\n2. 被人搜完問佢拎番警員編號，委任證，再打去警處check<br />\n<br />\nDresscode x3: <br />\nA. 着便衣裝扮: 深色衫，掛左牌在衫裡面<br />\nB. 全黑<br />\nC. 普通衫<br />\n<br />\nB+C 可以帶口罩，咩背囊，裝多啲無聊嘢等佢慢慢搜<br />\nM巾 condom 紙巾 薯片 etc<br />\n<br />\n另外可以拖埋喼<br />\n<br />\n使用語言: 英文，普通話"},{"pid":"d891134306a0911e1cae088d05b6b284b2fda722","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/br1vrjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbr1vrjr.png&h=d3a71424&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40cbc90a21961b36b07b96863d236fe8372ec0cd","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fba16ed3c3e9b247983b0f862ed1571d316b524d","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"一齊製作手提lock screen wallpaper以備於搜身及被捕後使用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15828a2c3b33d01be02d7003cb63f6f77abe9ac9","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47ac20efcdc1f3f85a76da1fd4288b9ee646d523","tid":1204280,"uid":128759,"like":0,"d